(6, 'Nc hoa nam Dior Sauvage Parfum', 'Mi hng nc hoa ca phin bn ln ny nh m li cun hn hai phin bn trc. V  lu hng ca nc hoa cng lu hn t 6-8 ting.', '<p><strong>Dior Sauvage Parfum</strong>&nbsp;ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; tip ni s th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng ca 2 &agrave;n anh i trc ca m&igrave;nh. &oacute; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; D<em>ior Sauvage Parfum EDP v&agrave; Dior Sauvage Parfum EDT</em>. Chai nc hoa n&agrave;y ra mt v&agrave;o nm 2019 &atilde; c n&acirc;ng cp l&ecirc;n. Mang n&eacute;t m thm hn nhng vn gi nguy&ecirc;n nhng th&agrave;nh phn then cht to n&ecirc;n thng hiu &ldquo;Lady Killer&rdquo;. Dior Sauvage Parfum l&agrave; mu nc hoa ly cm hng t tr&ecirc;n tho nguy&ecirc;n v&agrave;o ban &ecirc;m. B&ecirc;n di l&agrave; &aacute;nh la tri len li trong m&agrave;n &ecirc;m khin mi ngi vi n tng u ti&ecirc;n d&agrave;nh cho sn phm</p>', 18, 3950000, 3800000, 1, '2023-03-04 02:28:07', '2023-03-04 02:28:07', '/storage/uploads/2023/03/04/Dior-Sauvage-Parfum.jpg'),
(7, 'Giorgio Armani Acqua Di Gio Pour Homme', 'V  lu hng ca Gi trng s lu c trong khong 3-6 ting. Bn cnh , sau khi dng hn 6 ting ng h mnh vn cm nhn c mi hng thm nh', '<p><strong>Giorgio Armani Acqua Di Gio Pour Homme</strong>&nbsp;l&agrave; loi nc hoa ti trong khong t nc Ph&aacute;p. L&agrave; mt t nc vi ph th&ocirc;ng mu nc hoa nc ting tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n cu. Sn phm n&agrave;y c x&acirc;y dng thng hiu trong khong nm 1996. &atilde; c&oacute; rt nhiu kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng a chung v&agrave; tr l&agrave; mt tuyt t&aacute;c kinh in trong to&agrave;n cu nc hoa cao cp . C&aacute;c ngi t&igrave;nh mn nc hoa &atilde; t mt chic t&ecirc;n &lsquo; Gi&ograve; trng&rsquo; cc k&igrave; d thng cho d&ograve;ng nc hoa n&agrave;y. Vi thit k thun tu&yacute;, tinh t v&agrave; lch l&atilde;m.&nbsp;<em>Giorgio Armani Acqua Di Gio Pour Homme</em>&nbsp;to cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng cm gi&aacute;c ng cp mi l&uacute;c cm n&oacute;.</p>', 18, 2500000, 1690000, 1, '2023-03-04 02:30:45', '2023-03-04 02:30:45', '/storage/uploads/2023/03/04/nuoc-hoa-nam-giorgio-armani-acqua-di-gio-pour-homme-edt-100ml-62982a64e47f0-02062022101132.jpg'),
(8, 'Burberry The Beat For Men', 'Mi hng ca s i li, nng lng v tui tr to nn phn c th cho sn phm. Burberry The Beat For Men thch hp cho nhng chng trai s hu cuc sng bn rn hay vn ng lc  hng thm ca nc hoa s lm bn th gin d l bt c u.', '<p>Mt loi&nbsp;<strong>nc hoa cho nam</strong>&nbsp;ly cm hng trong khong &acirc;m nhc, &acirc;m thanh, c&aacute; t&iacute;nh, ngh thut v&agrave; b ngo&agrave;i. &atilde; to n&ecirc;n 1&nbsp;<strong><em>Burberry The Beat For Men</em></strong>&nbsp;ca ng&agrave;y ba nay. Ti trong khong nh&atilde;n hiu Burberry sau khi ra mt mu nc hoa cho n. Th&igrave; cm hng &oacute; vn c&ograve;n n&ecirc;n &atilde; cho ra mt nm v&agrave;o nm 2008 t&iacute;nh cho ti hin ti vn lu&ocirc;n nm trong Top nc hoa nam &aacute;ng d&ugrave;ng nht. Burberry The Beat For Men s hu tr&ecirc;n m&igrave;nh mt to lch l&atilde;m bi c&aacute;c mu k. L&agrave; biu tng ca nh&atilde;n hiu Burberry, phn dung dch mang m&agrave;u xanh lc nh.&nbsp;</p>', 18, 2500000, 1140000, 1, '2023-03-04 02:33:35', '2023-03-04 02:33:35', '/storage/uploads/2023/03/04/OIP.jpg'),
(9, 'Gucci Guilty Black', 'Nc hoa nam Gucci Guilty Black ph hp cho nhng chng trai vi phong cch ho phng, to bo v mt cht ngng cung.  lu hng cng nh cc dng EDT khc t 3-6 gi. V  ta hng ch 1 cnh tay. Bn cnh  sn phm vi hai dung tch cho bn chn lc 50ml v 90ml.', '<p>1 loi nc hoa mang n&eacute;t ti&ecirc;n tin li vng ch&uacute;t c in. Ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; nhc ti nc hoa nam Gucci Guilty Black. Ra mt c&oacute; mi ngi v&agrave; nm 2013 l&agrave; 1 trong nhng chic nc hoa nam t&aacute;o bo tng t c rng r&atilde;i gii thng tr&ecirc;n th gii.&nbsp;<strong>Gucci Guilty Black</strong>&nbsp;c mnh danh l&agrave; m&ugrave;i hng hp dn ca th k 21. S phi hp hai gam m&agrave;u xanh v&agrave; en c&agrave;ng l&agrave;m cho s t&aacute;o tn, mnh m. N&oacute; c biu hin r&otilde; hn, phn trng t&acirc;m ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; in ni logo ca nh&atilde;n h&agrave;ng Gucci to im nhn cho sn phm.</p>', 18, 2500000, 2000000, 1, '2023-03-04 02:35:14', '2023-03-04 02:35:14', '/storage/uploads/2023/03/04/1536303338.9734.png'),
(10, 'Bleu De Chanel EDP', 'loi nc hoa nam ny thch hp cho cc chng trai nng ng v hng thm mnh m s lm nhng c nng  gc lc sp bn. Mi hng thm mnh m nh vy u th 1-2 mang ting bay i c,  lu hng s gi cho bn t 7-12 ting ng h  bn lun t tn trong mi bui giao lu', '<p>loi&nbsp;<strong>nc hoa nam</strong>&nbsp;n&agrave;y th&iacute;ch hp cho c&aacute;c ch&agrave;ng trai nng ng v&igrave; hng thm mnh m s l&agrave;m nhng c&ocirc; n&agrave;ng  gc l&uacute;c sp bn. M&ugrave;i hng thm mnh m nh vy &acirc;u th 1-2 mang ting bay i c,  lu hng s gi cho bn t 7-12 ting ng h  bn lu&ocirc;n t t&iacute;n trong mi bui giao lu</p>', 18, 3000000, 2500000, 1, '2023-03-04 02:37:31', '2023-03-04 02:37:31', '/storage/uploads/2023/03/04/OIP (1).jpg'),
(11, 'Tom Ford Noir For Men', 'Nng  l EDP nn l dng nc hoa nam ny s lu hng cho bn khong 8-10 ting ng h. V  ko di hng thm cho bn sut c ngy.', '<p><strong>Nc hoa nam Tom Ford Noir For Men</strong>&nbsp;ti t nh&atilde;n hiu Tom Ford c ra mt v&agrave;o nm 2012. Vi n&eacute;t c in gia nhng th th&agrave;nh hin i b&acirc;y gi. D&ograve;ng nc hoa c ngo&agrave;i mt hi thun tu&yacute; phn thy tinh gam m&agrave;u ti  tr&ecirc;n vi t&ecirc;n sn phm m&agrave;u trng. B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, c&ograve;n v phn np sn phm c ngoi h&igrave;nh dng k nh khin vt bc sn phm hn. V m&ugrave;i hng cng s tri qua 3 tng lp c&oacute; cho bn s quyn r.</p>', 18, 4500000, 2950000, 1, '2023-03-04 02:40:55', '2023-03-04 02:40:55', '/storage/uploads/2023/03/04/Tom-Ford-Noir-for-Men-3-e1671720371600-300x300.jpg'),
(12, 'Calvin Klein CK  ONE', ' lu hng cng ko qu di t 3-6 ting. Nhng cng ko v th m mt i mi hng, CK One vn cn cht g  vng vt li trn ngi bn.', '<p><em><strong>Calvin Klein&nbsp;</strong></em><em><strong>CK &ndash; ONE</strong></em>&nbsp;l&agrave; d&ograve;ng nc hoa d&agrave;nh cho c nam v&agrave; n ti t nh&atilde;n hiu Calvin Klein<strong>.&nbsp;</strong>c ra mt v&agrave;o nm 1994, CK One &atilde; l&agrave;m cho &lsquo;chao o&rsquo;&rsquo; bn teen a chung nc hoa. V&agrave; &atilde; tr th&agrave;nh 1 tng &agrave;i trong thp ni&ecirc;n 90. CK One tinh t, quyn r kho&aacute;c tr&ecirc;n m&igrave;nh d&ograve;ng &aacute;o trng thy tinh m, phn np c l&agrave;m cho trong khong kim kh&iacute; bc s&aacute;ng. V&agrave; nm  v tr&iacute; ch&iacute;nh gia l&agrave; t&ecirc;n sn phm. Ba tng hng s khin cho bn cm nhn c tng ph&uacute;t chc c&oacute; ch&uacute;t mnh m, ph&oacute;ng kho&aacute;ng s hu ch&uacute;t g&igrave; y nh nh&otilde;m.</p>', 18, 1120000, 790000, 1, '2023-03-04 02:43:04', '2023-03-04 02:43:04', '/storage/uploads/2023/03/04/nuoc-hoa-calvin-klein-ck-ck-one-cho-ca-nam-va-nu-100ml-62070ada1c43b-12022022081818.jpg'),
(13, 'Valentino Uomo For Men', 'Nc hoa Valentino Uomo For Men s gi mi hng trong khong thi k 7-12 ting, bn b cho nhng cuc vui chi c ngy di hay cc ba tic xuyn m.', '<p><strong><em>Valentino Uomo For Men</em></strong>&nbsp;c nh&agrave; s&aacute;ng ch Olivier Polge to ra v&agrave; ti nm 2014 nh&atilde;n hiu Valentino &atilde; cho ra mt mu nc hoa nam n&agrave;y. Nc hoa nam c ly &yacute; tng t nhng g&igrave; c in trong &ocirc; th th&agrave;nh ph n&agrave;y, vng chc s s hu nhng qu&yacute; &ocirc;ng ham s gin d v&agrave; m&ugrave;i hng ca k&iacute; v&atilde;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>b ngo&agrave;i u chai h&igrave;nh v&ograve;m, th&acirc;n chai h&igrave;nh tr thng ng. Cht liu khin cho t thy tinh vi c&aacute;c ng v&acirc;n kim cng ni bt ph&iacute;a ngo&agrave;i biu th s nam t&iacute;nh v&agrave; mnh m.</p>', 18, 3000000, 2886615, 1, '2023-03-04 02:45:02', '2023-03-04 02:45:02', '/storage/uploads/2023/03/04/61ZcxnDFnAL._SR476,476_.jpg'),
(14, 'Versace Pour Homme', 'Versace Pour Homme tp kt cho mnh nhng nguyn t ca mt ngi n ng lch duyt, tinh t v giu tnh cm. Sn phm vi a dng dung tnh cho bn chn la nh 5ml, 30ml, 50ml, 100ml v 200ml.', '<p><em>Nc hoa nam Versace Pour Homme</em>&nbsp;c cho ra mt nm 2008 n t nh&atilde;n hiu Versace. M&ugrave;i hng nc hoa l&agrave; s h&ograve;a quyn ca chanh v&agrave;ng v&agrave; cam Bergamot. N&oacute; nh mt cn gi&oacute; m&aacute;t thi m&aacute;t gia d&ograve;ng nng ca m&ugrave;a h&egrave; n&oacute;ng bc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Th&ecirc;m phn thit k nc hoa cng rt thun tu&yacute;, c l&agrave;m cho trong khong thy tinh trong sut bn. Vi th nh&igrave;n thy phn dung dch m&agrave;u xanh nht b&ecirc;n trong. Bn s cm nhn c s ti m&aacute;t v&agrave; nh nh&otilde;m nhng vn to&aacute;t l&ecirc;n v nam t&iacute;nh bi c mu m&atilde; phn g&oacute;c cnh.</p>', 18, 3500000, 3199000, 1, '2023-03-04 02:46:42', '2023-03-04 02:46:42', '/storage/uploads/2023/03/04/OIP (2).jpg'),
(15, 'Hugo Boss Boss Bottled Oud Aromatic', 'Nc hoa nam Hugo Boss Boss Bottled Oud Aromatic l dng nc hoa dnh cho ngi phng ng n t thng hiu Hugo Boss. Chn l 1 thng hiu chuyn v cc mu nc hoa cao cp. Sn phm c ra mt va mi y vo nm 2019.', '<p><em>Hugo Boss Boss Bottled Oud Aromatic</em>&nbsp;c&oacute; hng thm chit xut kh&ocirc;ng ph th&ocirc;ng m&ugrave;i mix s hu nhau, th&iacute;ch hp cho c&aacute;c ngi &agrave;n &ocirc;ng lch duyt v&agrave; r&eacute;t mt.  lu hng s t 6-8 ting   bn tham gia mi ba tic hay i khin c ng&agrave;y d&agrave;i. Vi mu nc hoa n&agrave;y  ta hng s trong 1 c&aacute;nh tay ca bn,   ngi i din n tng c&oacute; bn.&nbsp;<strong>Hugo Boss Boss Bottled Oud Aromatic</strong>&nbsp;s l&agrave; tuyn la xut sc d&agrave;nh cho m&ugrave;a thu v&agrave; &ocirc;ng.</p>', 17, 2500000, 1990000, 1, '2023-03-04 02:48:04', '2023-03-04 02:48:04', '/storage/uploads/2023/03/04/OIP (3).jpg'),
(16, 'Good Girl Glorious Gold Carolina Herrera', 'Good Girl Glorious Gold Carolina Herrera c tip ni thnh cng ca Good Girl t khi ra mt 2016 tr danh ca hng.', '<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.thegioisonmoi.com/products/nuoc-hoa-good-girl-glorious-gold-carolina-herrera-edp-phien-ban-gioi-han-2019\">Good Girl Glorious Gold Carolina Herrera</a></strong>&nbsp;c tip ni th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng ca Good Girl t khi ra mt 2016 tr danh ca h&atilde;ng.&nbsp;Phi&ecirc;n bn Limited Edition&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://www.thegioisonmoi.com/products/nuoc-hoa-good-girl-glorious-gold-carolina-herrera-edp-phien-ban-gioi-han-2019\">Good Girl Glorious Gold</a></strong>&nbsp;si&ecirc;u phm guc nh v&agrave;ng c&ugrave;ng m&ugrave;i thm xut sc. Note hng cam bergamot, hnh nh&acirc;n quyn hoa hng v&agrave; hoa di&ecirc;n v. Ch&uacute;t vani v&agrave; cacao khin m&ugrave;i hng bng tr l&ecirc;n ngt ng&agrave;o, nng n&agrave;n y quyn r.</p>', 19, 3650000, NULL, 1, '2023-03-04 02:54:37', '2023-03-04 02:54:37', '/storage/uploads/2023/03/04/ti xung.jpg'),
(17, 'Chanel No.5 Eau De Parfum', 'y l loi nc hoa n trc nht ca hng Chanel ni danh. Chanel No.5 l mt sn phm huyn thoi hin nay. V  i cng mang nhiu c gi  mi  tui sut c mt thp k qua.', '<p>Hng trc ht m&agrave; ch&uacute;ng ta thun tin cm nhn l&agrave; tinh du hoa hng, Ylang-Ylang, hoa nh&agrave;i v&agrave; m&ugrave;i vani nh nh&agrave;ng, tinh t. Chanel No.5 em n hng gia mang tinh du hoa hng m c. B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, hng cui ca &agrave;n hng, x hng c&ugrave;ng vani. Ch&iacute;nh s pha trn kh&eacute;o l&eacute;o t nhiu d&ograve;ng tinh du kh&aacute;c nhau n&agrave;y. &atilde; khin cho Chanel No.5 mang 1 hng thm c bit. V&agrave; lu gi n tng kh&oacute; phai trong t&acirc;m tng ca rng r&atilde;i ngi.</p>', 19, 4000000, 3400000, 1, '2023-03-04 02:56:53', '2023-03-04 02:56:53', '/storage/uploads/2023/03/04/nuoc-hoa-nu-3.jpg'),
(18, 'D&G Velvet Cypress', 'Ra mt t nm 2017 nhng ti by gi D&G Velvet Cypress vn lun l s la chn ca phn ng bn gi. Chai nc hoa n c thit k l thy tinh sang trng, y cun ht.', '<p>Ra mt t nm 2017 nhng ti b&acirc;y gi D&amp;G Velvet Cypress vn lu&ocirc;n l&agrave; s la chn ca phn &ocirc;ng bn g&aacute;i. Chai nc hoa n c&oacute; thit k l thy tinh sang trng, y cun h&uacute;t.&nbsp;</p>', 19, 4000000, 3450000, 1, '2023-03-04 02:58:34', '2023-03-04 02:58:34', '/storage/uploads/2023/03/04/OIP (4).jpg'),
(19, 'Dior Jadore', 'khi  cp n nhn hng Dior t gi th ko ngi no l ko bit ti loi nc hoa n. Jadore s hu mi hng quyn r, ngt ngo v v cng sang trng.', '<p>J&rsquo;adore em li s h&ograve;a quyn gia m&ugrave;i hng ho hng Damascena Th Nh K. V&agrave; c&ugrave;ng vi tinh cht &agrave;m hng Sri Lanka v&agrave; hoa nh&agrave;i Grasse. &ocirc;ng o c phi hp li to n&ecirc;n hng thm c th&ugrave; trong J&rsquo;adore. N&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; nng m&agrave; biu t s ti mi, nh nh&agrave;ng v&agrave; kh&ocirc;n c&ugrave;ng n t&iacute;nh. Sn phm c ngoi h&igrave;nh c&oacute; v ngo&agrave;i sang chnh. Cng vi ng cong hp dn va s hu phong c&aacute;ch ti&ecirc;n tin pha ch&uacute;t c in b&ecirc;n trong.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>iu c bit cho mu nc hoa n&agrave;y &oacute; l&agrave; c&aacute;c bn d&ugrave;ng th 5ml. i vi hng n&agrave;ng c&oacute; th b t&uacute;i d d&agrave;ng khi vn ng bt c &acirc;u c&oacute; l nc hoa n mini Dior J&rsquo;adore n&agrave;y.</p>', 19, 3700000, 3450000, 1, '2023-03-04 03:00:29', '2023-03-04 03:00:29', '/storage/uploads/2023/03/04/nuoc-hoa-nu-dior-j-adore-edp-100ml-63b3e7af56598-03012023153039.png'),
(20, 'Gucci Flora', 'Gucci Flora l mu nc hoa n say m ca nhng c nng tui mi ln. Nhn hng cao cp nc ting th gii Gucci lun bit ly lng khch hng.', '<p>Hng nc hoa c tng h&ograve;a trong khong rng r&atilde;i c&aacute;i tinh du. Chng hn nh hng cam qu&yacute;t, hoa c&aacute;i n rt ti mi. Gucci Flora mang li hng gia l&agrave; m&ugrave;i thm ca ho hng v&agrave; hoa mc t. V&agrave; hng kt th&uacute;c hng ci vi g &agrave;n hng, hoc hng v&agrave; tuyt t&ugrave;ng. Mu nc hoa n n&agrave;y gi c m&ugrave;i hng rt l&acirc;u. Vi  lan ta mnh v&agrave; kh&ocirc;n c&ugrave;ng m n&ecirc;n ph&ugrave; hp s dng trong nhng ng&agrave;y m&ugrave;a &ocirc;ng gi&aacute; lnh.</p>', 19, 2150000, 1750000, 1, '2023-03-04 03:01:54', '2023-03-04 03:01:54', '/storage/uploads/2023/03/04/nuoc-hoa-nu-gucci-flora-gorgeous-gardenia-edt-100ml-620a12117a931-14022022152553.jpg'),
(21, 'Dior Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet', 'y l dng nc hoa n khn xit ni danh. V c nh khng th vng mt trn cc k m phm ca bit bao c gi. Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet mang n mi hng khn cng thanh mt, nh nhng.', '<p>Trong khong hng u ti hng gia c phi hp. Bi tinh du hoa c&aacute;i n, hu&ecirc; hng c&ugrave;ng ch&uacute;t m&ugrave;i v ti m&aacute;t ca cam Bergamot. Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet cho m&ugrave;i hng cui l&agrave; x hng trng em n s mm mi, nh nh&agrave;ng. T &oacute;, gi&uacute;p nhng c&ocirc; n&agrave;ng vui v, thnh thi. Hn. Miss Dior ko qu&aacute; ngt hay nng m&agrave; ch du nh, thanh khit. N&ecirc;n rt th&iacute;ch hp mang nhng bn mi ln u s dng nc hoa. Ch&iacute;nh cho n&ecirc;n, ko c&oacute; g&igrave; l&agrave; kh&oacute; hiu l&uacute;c Miss Dior lu&ocirc;n nm trong top sn phm nc hoa n b&aacute;n chy v&agrave; c a dng c&ocirc; g&aacute;i ham.</p>', 19, 3050000, 2800000, 1, '2023-03-04 03:04:23', '2023-03-04 03:04:23', '/storage/uploads/2023/03/04/nuoc-hoa-dior-miss-dior-blooming-bouquet-100ml-5cf1f44ef1854-01062019104310.jpg'),
(22, 'Carolina Herrera Good Girl Lgre Eau De Parfum', 'Gi cm, quyn r, thu ht', '<p><strong>Good Girl Legere</strong>&nbsp;l&agrave; s h&ograve;a quyn c&aacute;c hng hoa c ti s&aacute;ng, hng thc phm ngt ng&agrave;o  ri quyn r, l&ocirc;i cun hn ngi n kh&ocirc;ng th cng li. Nt hng u m ra vi ngc lan t&acirc;y. Sau &oacute; nhng ch cho v p tinh khit ca nh&agrave;i trng c&ograve;n lan sang hng gia, kt hp vi hoa hu y m&ecirc; m, c&oacute; th l&agrave;m ng&atilde; gc nhng tr&aacute;i tim cung m&ugrave;i hng c &aacute;o t chic gi&agrave;y cao g&oacute;t&nbsp;<strong>Good Girl</strong>&nbsp;sang chnh n&agrave;y. Hng cui dai dng vi u tonka v&agrave; g &agrave;n hng to n&ecirc;n v p ca&nbsp;<strong>Good Girl Legere</strong>.</p>', 17, 670000, 470000, 1, '2023-03-04 03:09:51', '2023-03-04 03:09:51', '/storage/uploads/2023/03/04/nuoc-hoa-carolina-herrera-good-girl-legere-eau-de-parfum-10ml-dang-lan-63297b8c27daf-20092022153628.jpg'),
(23, 'Prada Candy Eau De Parfum Spray Pen For Women', 'Ngt ngo, cun ht, n tnh', '<p><strong>Nc hoa Prada Candy Eau De Parfum Spray Pen For Women </strong>&nbsp;l&agrave; chai nc hoa mi c ra mt trong nm 2021 ca thng hiu&nbsp;<strong>Prada</strong>. Hng thm thm ngt ng&agrave;o ca nh&oacute;m hng hoa c phng &ocirc;ng cho n&agrave;ng th&ecirc;m cun h&uacute;t, n t&iacute;nh.</p>', 20, 790000, 470000, 1, '2023-03-04 03:13:13', '2023-03-04 03:13:13', '/storage/uploads/2023/03/04/nuoc-hoa-nu-prada-candy-eau-de-parfum-spray-pen-fo-women-0-33-oz-10-ml-dang-xit-63b689eac2c2d-05012023152722.jpg'),
